Package org.jamsim.ascape.stats

Collection of simulation values.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
StatsFunction<T> Returns a simulation double value on a scape member.
StatsPredicate<T> Tests a scape member.
 

Class Summary
CollectorFunction<T> Collect data values on a subset of the scape.
CollectorFunctionPerIteration<T> Collect data values per iteration.
StatsFunctionRow<T> A stats row representing a function and a mutable denominator value.
StatsPredicateRow<T> A stats row that represents a predicate, a denominator function, and a denominator value.
StatsRows Collection of CollectorFunctions created from StatsFunctionRows or StatsPredicateRows.
 

Package org.jamsim.ascape.stats Description

Collection of simulation values.
